Set Up Einstein Discovery for Reports
Einstein Discovery for Reports is available after enabling CRM Analytics and assigning the Can Run Einstein Discovery for Reports permission.
Available in Lightning Experience, Developer Edition, and Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions.
To set up Einstein Discovery for Reports: Manage CRM Analytics
Assign a permission set to users that includes the Can Run Einstein Discovery for Reports permission.
The standard permission set CRM Analytics Plus User is available with the CRM Analytics Plus license.
After enabling CRM Analytics and assigning permission sets, users have access to Einstein Discovery for Reports.
